section.section:
This subsection applies to certificates issued on or after January 1, 1998, for which reserves are computed on:
the Commissioners 1941 Standard Ordinary Mortality Table;
the Commissioners 1941 Standard Industrial Table;
the Commissioners 1958 Standard Ordinary Mortality Table;
the Commissioners 1980 Standard Mortality Table; or
any more recent table authorized for use under § 5-304(b) of this article.
